name: We are not here anymore.
description:
The past is here too, but we can't see it, isn't material. We are a representation of it, we exist because of what happened, we are because of that, but we should not live for that. 
The idea of past is very complex, because we need to learn our mistakes, and at the same time, we should not live in there because is heartbraker, is gone, there is nothing we can't change, only the future is in our hands, and not completely... 

Created by Ego Rangel 2021. From the series Fake Paintings.
